            <title>[LU-1401] sanity test passed but it&apos;s marked ABORT</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1401</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Maloo test log shows sanity test passed, but it&apos;s marked ABORTED.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/2b2ebe70-9bad-11e1-a0a0-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/2b2ebe70-9bad-11e1-a0a0-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
